snippet.textDisplay:
Main use bhool chuka hoon, jo tha mera tha,  
Teri yaadon ka rang ab udaas hai, khata.  
Jitni dafa tu yaad aayi thi, utni hi baar,  
Main ne chhupayi apni dard bhari ik zindagi ki daar.  

Waqt ne sab kuch mita diya, sab kuch badal gaya,  
Ab teri yaadon ka koi asar nahi, sab kuch khatam gaya.  
Par kabhi kabhi, ek purani dhun ke saath,  
Dil mein teri tasveer phir se aati hai saath.
